data.description: Motivated sellers!! Charming, well maintained 3 Br, 2.5 BA home in the highly sought after neighborhood of Brighton Crossing. The open floor plan is great for entertaining with stainless steel Bosch appliances. This home is pre-wired for sound inside and out, has a smart thermostat, video doorbell and video surveillance all around. Convenient powder bath on the main level. The spacious primary bedroom features a vaulted ceiling with fan, 2 closets, double vanity and large shower. Two additional bedrooms and a full bathroom complete the upstairs. Private fenced yard with oversized patio perfect for summer BBQ's plus a second side yard/dog run with access from the built in dog kennel in the garage. The partially unfinished basement is ready for additional living or flex space. The front yard is professionally maintained for low maintenance living. Move -in for the holidays & enjoy access to the clubhouse, 2 gyms, dog park, outdoor swimming pools in 2024!!
